```

**`client/src/components/VisitProfile/Visitprofile.jsx`** -- Same pattern as above, add `StreakBadge` in the visited profile name row (around line 208-215). Use `useStreakData(visitedUserId)` to fetch the visited user's streak.

**`client/src/components/HomePage/Editor/RichTextEditor.jsx`** -- After a successful save (inside `handleClickSave`, after `saveData` returns), check if the response includes streak data and show the milestone toast if applicable:

```javascript
