```

**`client/src/components/SidebarOpinions/OpinionsEditor.jsx`** -- Same pattern after successful opinion save. Invalidate streak query and check for milestone.

**`client/src/components/HomePage/Home.jsx`** -- This is the main layout that wraps the sidebar. Add streak data fetching here and pass it down. Also, add `StreakMilestoneToast` state management at this level so milestones can be triggered from any child editor:

```jsx
